rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）就追，搞到有d...唉我都唔識講呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c2c77bb2a7afb2a60e03d1ad647a6e98b7c696","tid":147840,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:42:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>痛過後不懂得再愛人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對愛情失去信心？</blockquote><br />\n以前真係愛佢先追，宜家只要有少少好感（即係靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）就追，搞到有d...唉我都唔識講呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時太鍾意反而唔會想追<br />\n因為驚失去<br />\n反而只有好感又未算好有感情果種先會追"},{"pid":"803b49423f2cc8f5bd496a16402037951954d576","tid":147840,"uid":14885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T07:34:59.000Z","msg":"做咗煙鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a193278e19ab69c1eac8c3ebd10f239812c8a7a","tid":147840,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T12:27:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做咗煙鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一支點解食"},{"pid":"f007031e05393a3dceaa7040409a346298ba0f1d","tid":147840,"uid":57857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T12:37:58.000Z","msg":"以為自己大左返工可以:<br />\n<br />\n中學嘅老死可以個個留住(有啲大學就冇左)<br />\n繼續keep住成日打波成日陪friend<br />\n可以唔洗戴假面具對人學人賣笑<br />\n可以憑努力有料就上到位<br />\n可以返份前途錢途同有實質社會貢獻嘅工最後都係只有為數字勞碌<br />\n<br />\nbtw樓主我都係細個唔肯係街痾屎, 直至有一次又係肚痾搞唔掂迫自己去左, 好記得我死忍住係廁版鋪左幾層紙巾先坐落去"},{"pid":"086f4bb1e730fd49b645e258a94d435443904997","tid":147840,"uid":26401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T12:46:36.000Z","msg":"細個諗住大個唔會食煙，點知而家變左煙鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}